.TH bop 1  "bop 0.1.0" 
.SH NAME
bop \- Battery Optimization Project \- hardware\-aware power tuning for Linux laptops
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbop\fR [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Battery Optimization Project \- hardware\-aware power tuning for Linux laptops
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Output as JSON instead of formatted tables
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
bop\-audit(1)
Scan system and show power optimization findings
.TP
bop\-apply(1)
Apply recommended optimizations
.TP
bop\-monitor(1)
Real\-time power draw monitoring (RAPL + battery)
.TP
bop\-revert(1)
Undo all changes from saved state
.TP
bop\-status(1)
Show current optimization state and detect drift
.TP
bop\-wake(1)
Manage expansion card wakeup sources (Framework\-specific)
.TP
bop\-completions(1)
Generate shell completions
